    <p class="description fade-in" style="--delay: 0.1s">
      I’M CELINA—A UX ENGINEER WITH A MASTER’S IN HUMAN-CENTERED DESIGN &
      ENGINEERING. I BRIDGE DESIGN AND CODE TO CREATE INTERACTIVE, ACCESSIBLE,
      AND SCALABLE USER EXPERIENCES. FROM DESIGN SYSTEMS TO RAPID PROTOTYPING, I
      BRING IDEAS TO LIFE THROUGH FRONTEND DEVELOPMENT, MICROINTERACTIONS, AND
      EMERGING TECH LIKE 3D PRINTING AND HARDWARE PROTOTYPING.
    </p>
    <p class="description"></p>

